************ WebDownloader for X Window system ****************
************ This program have no name yet :(( ****************

Autor:
    Koshelev Maxim 
    e-mail: mdem@chat.ru
    second e-mail: chuchelo@krasu.ru
    home page: http://www.krasu.ru/soft/chuchelo

Main features:
    multithread;
    downloading via both HTTP and FTP protocols;
    recursive downloading through both ftp and http protocol;
    queue of downloads;
    mask support;
    ftp and http proxy support;
    X Window user-friendly grahpical interface;
    supporting resuming files after connections breaks (useful for far sites);
    logs for all downloads;
    common log;
    mass downloading function;
    traffic throttle;
    ftp search;

Other features:
    much more stable than other such programs for Linux :))
